title: Week 9 NFL Recap, Analysis; Browns about to blow up (Football 11/4)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 9 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 12 games on the Sunday slate including Pats-Ravens (2:00), Jets-Dolphins (17:45), Browns-Broncos (29:45), Vikings-Chiefs (46:30), Bears-Eagles (52:00), Packers-Chargers (1:01:45), Raiders-Lions (1:09:15), Colts-Steelers (1:15:00), Texans-Jags (1:22:15), Bucs-Seahawks (1:30:00), Titans-Panthers (1:36:45) and Redskins-Bills (1:40:15).
